<CustomPageWithReturn ID="x32521" Name="Pathway Registration" Layout="general_content.xsl"><Title type="string" label="Title" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Pathway Registration</Title><Abstract type="string" label="Abstract" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">How to find and register for BYU-Idaho Pathway courses</Abstract><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="LeftNavGroup" label="Left Nav Return" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="true"><ParentName type="string" label="Parent Name" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">Online Support Center</ParentName><xPower Type="Link" Link="x28630" Name="Link" label="Link" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true" LinkText="Online Support Center" Target="" Expanded="false" URL=""/></xPower><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<p>Watch this video for detailed instructions on how to find the courses you should register for and how to use the registration system. If you are having trouble watching the video, <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I-BOivaZogg">Try the YouTube version</a> or view the <a href="x30317.xml">text instructions</a>.</p>
<p>To find or register for online courses:</p>
<ol>
<li>Log-in through <a href="https://web.byui.edu/services/login?RedirectURL=https://my.byui.edu" target="_blank">my.byui.edu</a></li>
<li>Click on the blue "<strong>STUDENT</strong>" tab</li>
<li>Click on the "<strong>Course Search</strong>" icon in the  Registration box on the bottom left side of the page</li>
<li>Complete the following fields:                                                             
<ul>
<li><strong>Term</strong>:  Choose desired term (Ex: Spring Semester 2012)</li>
<li><strong>Sub Program:</strong> "Academic Start ACST")</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>This should give you a listing of online  courses being offered that semester.</li>
<li>It is also very important to pay special attention to the blue notes in the registration system. Be sure to register for the correct course based on your Pathway location.<br /><br /><img alt="blue notes" height="97" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Online Learning/PathwayCurrentStu/Screen shot 2012-03-19 at 1.13.58 PM.png" width="675" /></li>
<li>To add a course, click the "Add" checkbox next to the desired course  and  section; then click the "Add Courses" button at the bottom of the  page. The "Add" box will not be  available until your <a href="http://www.byui.edu/registrarsoffice/RegSchedule.htm">registration period</a> opens.</li>
</ol>
